<help communications idea>

These methods log comments to files that I try to check
fairly often.  Please put any ideas or bugs or typos into
these commands, or email the implementor
(greear@cyberhighway.net).

syntax:  idea  [message_text]
syntax:  bug   [message_text]

example:  idea You should create a spell to teleport objects.
example:  bug I tried the 'idea' command, and it crashed us!

<color=red>
See Also:  olc
</color></help>


